sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Spark Operator Controller<br/>8080/metrics 8081/health
    participant SparkSubmit as spark-submit<br/>(local process)
    participant Driver as Spark Driver Pod<br/>7078/TCP RPC
    participant Executors as Spark Executor Pods<br/>7079/TCP Block Mgr
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: SparkApplication Submission and Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: POST SparkApplication CR<br/>Auth: Bearer token / client cert
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-sparkapplication<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Defaulted SparkApplication
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-sparkapplication<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI-->>User: SparkApplication created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch SparkApplication<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: SparkApplication event

    Controller->>SparkSubmit: Invoke spark-submit<br/>(local process exec)
    SparkSubmit->>K8sAPI: Create Driver Pod<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Note right of Webhook: Injects 25+ mutations:<br/>env vars, volumes, ports,<br/>init/sidecar containers,<br/>GPU, Prometheus, security,<br/>scheduling, DNS config
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Driver Pod

    Driver->>K8sAPI: Create Executor Pods<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Executor Pods

    Driver->>Executors: Spark RPC<br/>7078/TCP HTTP (no encryption)
    Executors->>Driver: Block transfer<br/>7079/TCP HTTP (no encryption)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update SparkApplication status<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: ScheduledSparkApplication Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: POST ScheduledSparkApplication CR
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch ScheduledSparkApplication
    Note right of Controller: Cron trigger fires
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create child SparkApplication CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Note right of Controller: Follows Flow 1 steps above
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Enforce concurrency policy<br/>+ cleanup history

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Spark Connect Server

    User->>K8sAPI: POST SparkConnect CR
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>(executor template)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Server Pod
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Server Service<br/>(ports: 7078, 7079, 4040, 15002)
    User->>Driver: gRPC/HTTP2 connect<br/>15002/TCP (no encryption)
    Driver->>Executors: Spark RPC<br/>7078/TCP, 7079/TCP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Monitoring

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>No auth
